Usage: check_module_model [-help] -cell <string> [-out_file <string>]
                          -ref_tag <string> [-slack_threshold <string>]
                          [-type <string>]

-help                         # Prints out the command usage
-cell <string>                # Specifies ILM cell name that will be validated
                              # (string, required)
-out_file <string>            # Specifies the output report file
                              # (string, optional)
-ref_tag <string>             # Specifies reference tag name of the reference
                              # ILM model (string, required)
-slack_threshold <string>     # Specified the slack threshold for reporting
                              # number mismatched slacks over threshold
                              # (string, optional)
-type <string>                # Specifies type for model checking. It can be
                              # ilm, pnr, or flexilm (string, optional)